article_title: White House's Obamacare bracket features twerking and ducks for 'free' birth control
article_text:
White House staffers have published a list of gifs and cat pictures to promote Obamacare to young people.

The list, titled "The 16 Sweetest Reasons to Get Covered," is now on the official White House website and features a duck promoting free birth control and a girl attempting to twerk on a sink before getting hurt.
